text: Ara na ache tadera upara yara eseche tomara nikata yena tumi tadera bahana dana kara ebam tumi balecha, amara kache emana kona bastu ne'i ye, tara upara tomadera sa'oyara karaba takhana tara phire geche athaca takhana tadera cokha diye asru ba'itechila e duhkhe ye, tara emana kona bastu pacche na ya byaya karabe.
